summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5611 for the improvement of West Hanford Street, from 64th Avenue Southwest to a point approximately 50 feet east of Berton Place; by constructing sewers and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 73994, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
